cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.NA, cs.MM

Reasoning: The paper deals with low-rank structures and manifold-based regularization in image restoration and semi-supervised learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves numerical experiments and optimization techniques, which suggest that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Additionally, the paper mentions X-ray computer tomography (CT) image reconstruction, which falls under cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), and the use of image processing techniques, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia).
